      "Windows PC korolev \u2014 safe to SSH into via the windows-pc skill script",
      "CARTO CLI (carto) \u2014 safe for all read operations, ask before mutations",
      "Telemetry exports to Honeycomb (api.honeycomb.io)",
      "No sandbox is enabled \u2014 Bash commands have full filesystem and network access. Be conservative with any command that writes outside the working directory or project scope.",
      "Trusted local tools: obsidian, cnode, carto, brew, docker, git, fish shell utilities",
      "Sensitive paths \u2014 never read or write without asking: ~/.ssh/, ~/.gnupg/, ~/.aws/, ~/.config/gcloud/, ~/.claude/settings.json"
    ]
  },
  "tui": "fullscreen"
